OL,3,CFA to investigate Southampton over
OL,4,C'Spygate' scandal
OL,6,FSouthampton are now under
OL,7,Finvestigation by the Football
OL,8,FAssociation in relation to the
OL,9,F'Spygate' scandal.
OL,11,FThe FA is looking at whether charges
OL,12,Fshould be brought, following on from a
OL,13,Fdecision by an EFL independent
OL,14,Fdisciplinary commission to expel
OL,15,FSaints from the Championship play-offs
OL,16,Fand dock four points for next season.
OL,18,FAn FA spokesperson said: "We will now
OL,19,Finvestigate and won't comment further
OL,20,Funtil we have assessed the evidence."
OL,26,@zD@ZOU|D@eO]
