OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779393955
OL,3,CFA to investigate Southampton over
OL,4,C'Spygate' scandal
OL,6,FSouthampton admitted to spying on a
OL,7,Ftraining session held by play-off semi-
OL,8,Ffinal opponents Middlesbrough earlier
OL,9,Fthis month, as well as one held by
OL,10,FOxford in December and an Ipswich
OL,11,Fsession in April.
OL,13,FAll three instances occurred following
OL,14,Fthe appointment of Tonda Eckert as
OL,15,Fhead coach in early December.
OL,17,FThe club's appeal against the sanction
OL,18,Fimposed by the commission was
OL,19,Fdismissed on Wednesday night, with
OL,20,FBoro now replacing Saints in
OL,21,FSaturday's play-off final against Hull.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
