PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779393955
OL,3,CFA to investigate Southampton over
OL,4,C'Spygate' scandal
OL,6,FSouthampton chief executive Phil
OL,7,FParsons said the sanctions imposed
OL,8,Fwere "manifestly disproportionate".
OL,10,FKicking them out of the play-offs also
OL,11,Fdenies them a shot at a Premier League
OL,12,Fplace and with it an estimated
OL,13,F#200million in additional revenue as a
OL,14,Fminimum.
OL,16,FSaints' player of the year Leo Scienza
OL,17,Fdescribed the punishment as
OL,18,F"heartbreaking" and said the club's
OL,19,Ffans "definitely deserved better".
