OL,3,CFA to investigate Southampton over
OL,4,C'Spygate' scandal
OL,6,F"We gave everything for this dream,"
OL,7,Fhe posted on Instagram.
OL,9,F"Day after day, sacrifice after
OL,10,Fsacrifice, always believing we could
OL,11,Fbring this club back to where it
OL,12,Fbelongs.
OL,14,F"For me, the dream of playing in the
OL,15,FPremier League was something I fought
OL,16,Ffor with everything I had.
OL,18,F"That's why this pain cuts so deep."
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@dO]qD@AOUvD@AOUzD@dO]
